text: Irfanullah Shah (born 5 May 1995) is a cricketer from Bannu, Pakistan. He made his Twenty20 debut on 26 August 2016 for Federally Administered Tribal Areas in the 2016–17 Cool & Cool Present Jazz National T20 Cup. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Federally Administered Tribal Areas cricketers Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:People from Bannu District
